Diabetes mellitus type 2 and abnormal glucose metabolism in the setting of human 
immunodeficiency virus.

Hadigan C(1), Kattakuzhy S(2).

Author information:
(1)Laboratory of Immunoregulation, National Institute of Allergy and Infectious 
Diseases, NIH, 10 Center Drive, Bethesda, MD 20892, USA. Electronic address: 
hadiganc@niaid.nih.gov.
